            <lg xml:id="TK978">
<l>paṇiyumā meṉṟum perumai ciṟumai </l>
<l>yaṇiyumān taṉṉai viyantu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great will always humble himself but the mean will exalt himself in self-admiration.</l>
            </lg>
